summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Library Board to purchase lots nine (9), ten (10), eleven (11), and twelve (12), and the west half of lot thirteen (13), block thirty-four (34), Denny & Hoyt's Addition to the City of Seattle, in the City of Seattle, for a sum not to exceed three thousand ($3,000.00) Dollars for library purposes, payment to be made from the library fund, and declaring an emergency.
